Privacy Policy for Ultimate Financial Calculator - All-in-One Finance Toolkit

Effective Date: August 1st, 2024

1. Introduction

Welcome to Ultimate Financial Calculator - All-in-One Finance Toolkit ("we," "our," or "us"). We are committed to protecting your privacy and providing a safe, useful experience for all our users. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use our mobile application.

2. Information We Collect

Our app is designed to respect your privacy. We do not collect any personal information unless it is necessary for the functionality of the app. The information we may collect includes:

a) User-Provided Data: Any financial data you input into the calculators for the purpose of performing calculations. This data is stored locally on your device using SwiftData and is not transmitted to our servers.

b) Usage Data: We may collect anonymous usage statistics to improve the app's performance and user experience. This data does not identify individual users.

3. How We Use Your Information

We use the information collected solely for the purpose of providing and improving our service:

a) To perform calculations based on the data you input
b) To save your favorite calculations locally on your device
c) To analyze app usage patterns and improve our features

4. Data Storage and Security

All user-provided data is stored locally on your device using SwiftData. We do not have access to this data, nor is it transmitted to our servers or any third parties.

5. Third-Party Services

Our app does not integrate with any third-party services that would have access to your data.

6. Children's Privacy

Our app is not directed to children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If you are a parent or guardian and believe that your child has provided us with personal information, please contact us.

7. Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page and updating the "Effective Date" at the top of this policy.

8. Your Rights

As all data is stored locally on your device, you have full control over your data. You can delete all data associated with the app by deleting the app from your device.

9. Contact Us

If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:

tolgapekyorur@gmail.com

